Name: Cyber City
About the game: Cyber City is a role play based cyberpunk style game where you get to explore the city, learn the rules that govern it and overcome them to feel like the most influence and famous person. The city is very diverse and gives plenty oppurtunities for gaining fame and riches. You just need to be focused and determined in order to see them. Go crazy in the strip clubs full of hot women! Sexy nude girls will do anything you want and keep your company. Party and enjoy! Prove your strength on the Arena, fight your way to the very top. Choose your weapon, create your tactic and don’t let your guard down. Thousands of people are watching. One fail could end your cariere. When you’ll get filthy rich, all the doors in the City will be open to you.
